## Limitations

The report is limited by the availability of sources and the potential bias in the perspectives presented. The complexity of racism means that not all aspects can be covered comprehensively in a single report. Additionally, the reliance on online sources may not capture the full academic discourse on the topic. Further research, including peer-reviewed studies, would provide a more robust understanding of the origins of racism.